magisk-dropbear
===============

This repository packages the Dropbear SSH suite
(https://github.com/mkj/dropbear) as a Magisk module for Android.

It contains only build scripts, a Magisk module template, and one small
Android-specific patch against upstream. The Dropbear source itself is NOT
stored in this repository — it is pulled in at build time as a git
submodule under dropbear/, pointing unmodified at the upstream tree.


